Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===MAIN===
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.04,0:01:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡辛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.07,0:02:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的手在毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.65,0:02:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 露娜一定会阻止毁灭的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.78,0:02:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要相信露娜 毁灭立刻就会...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.15,0:02:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊 毁灭停止了 毁灭停止了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.70,0:02:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点锈迹也没有！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.67,0:02:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想死的家伙就去露娜那里吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.64,0:02:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去接受露娜的治愈！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.87,0:02:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露娜还活着？ 为什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.18,0:02:47.19,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(579,390)}往事历历在目
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.37,0:02:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治愈？ 这个世界还有治愈存在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.09,0:03:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去露娜那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.24,0:03:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 只是谣传而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.15,0:03:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为露娜被你杀死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.63,0:03:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此毁灭才会开始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.53,0:03:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露娜还活着的话 你觉得自己犯下的罪过就能一笔勾销？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.74,0:03:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这是不可能的 露娜已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.72,0:03:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不希望露娜还活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.32,0:03:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话我的姐姐是为了什么而死...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.80,0:03:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又是为了什么而复仇...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.17,0:04:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去找露娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.18,0:04:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都在那之后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.40,0:04:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃亡者只有死路一条
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.79,0:04:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么露娜能阻止毁灭 胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.40,0:04:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要相信迪奥大人就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.31,0:04:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个露娜还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.55,0:04:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治愈机械人和人类吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.89,0:04:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和过去的露娜一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.00,0:05:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 不过当时并没有发生毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.76,0:05:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布莱金格·保斯为何要下命抹杀露娜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.45,0:05:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时我想都没有去想过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.28,0:05:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过现在你应该明白了 王只能有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.16,0:05:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露娜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.39,0:05:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露娜...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.20,0:05:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧吉 露娜是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.76,0:05:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在说露娜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.11,0:06:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺诈者、神经错乱者或者是亡灵 就是这类的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.50,0:06:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.25,0:06:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露娜被卡辛杀死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.63,0:06:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被那个卡辛...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.74,0:06:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧吉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑吧 笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.32,0:06:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累了吧 林檎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.35,0:06:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找个地方休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使见到露娜 即使知道了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.71,0:06:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只会明白一切和我说的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.71,0:06:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不害怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.54,0:07:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的我的话会害怕 但是现在不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.07,0:07:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我目睹了世界的毁灭 并且想阻止毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.51,0:07:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心 那里的地面很脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.43,0:07:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我目睹了世界的毁灭 并且想阻止毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.16,0:07:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此我首先要知道发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.42,0:08:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使露娜还活着 即便如此 世界的毁灭也还是你的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.87,0:08:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨天车子抛锚 真是不走运
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.90,0:08:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧吉 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.91,0:08:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 马上就好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.56,0:08:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.14,0:08:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林檎 会淋湿的 进车去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.46,0:08:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 没事 我喜欢雨天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.42,0:08:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为在雨中 世界看起来是如此闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.87,0:08:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨声我也喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.39,0:08:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.77,0:09:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.82,0:09:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.48,0:09:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔 看见了 看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.32,0:09:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看见了 看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.85,0:09:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是卡辛 卡辛在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.80,0:09:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林檎 出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.88,0:09:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧吉 卡辛在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.19,0:09:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.39,0:09:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里 卡辛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.45,0:09:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等等 林檎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.65,0:09:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧吉也过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.19,0:09:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.91,0:09:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌的雨势
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.18,0:09:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡辛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.50,0:09:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡辛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.31,0:09:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林檎 林檎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.39,0:09:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摔倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.35,0:10:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林檎 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.43,0:10:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 你看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.42,0:10:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很美吧 我在那边捡到的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.45,0:10:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 林檎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.39,0:10:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浑身湿透了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.15,0:10:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.04,0:10:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能没事 也不穿大衣 生锈了怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.10,0:10:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找个地方弄干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.86,0:10:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠近火堆比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.74,0:10:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林檎 不要乱动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.62,0:10:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.78,0:11:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林檎 毁灭的程度比之前更严重了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.89,0:11:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 抬起手来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.68,0:11:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.69,0:11:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林檎 这是血吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.76,0:11:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真的 不过不痛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.40,0:11:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.61,0:11:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你生锈了...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.50,0:11:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经弄干了吧 把衣服穿好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.70,0:11:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.24,0:11:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.56,0:12:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思打扰了 请让我也避一下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.57,0:12:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在毁灭的身体受不了这种雨的刺激
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.80,0:13:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 凉凉的 好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.07,0:13:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉兹你看 琉兹看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.35,0:13:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么那样盯着他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.30,0:13:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进来之后一直盯着卡辛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.34,0:13:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.89,0:13:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要去露娜那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.01,0:13:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定是冒牌货哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.23,0:13:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.09,0:13:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.65,0:14:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为被卡辛杀死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.32,0:14:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？ 为什么你会知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这些小贝壳 这个样子 一定...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.74,0:14:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊 果然很美
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的露娜是否是真的 去看看就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.27,0:14:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治愈又是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.82,0:14:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡辛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.97,0:14:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会 难道说...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.42,0:14:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.01,0:14:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.44,0:14:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布莱金格·保斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.67,0:15:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡辛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.19,0:15:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你是想起一点来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.68,0:15:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正终归要去做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.67,0:15:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给这个世界做个了断
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.87,0:15:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.02,0:15:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.21,0:15:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师？ 难道说...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.19,0:15:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 就是这位老师制造了卡辛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.39,0:16:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经 自以为是的机械人想成为神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.89,0:16:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 更加荒诞的事情 想制造出神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.56,0:16:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无尽的生命 早已经得到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.97,0:16:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为医学的进步 即使是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.37,0:16:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除非是运气很差 否则也是不会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.08,0:16:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有一点是机械人无论如何也办不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.28,0:16:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繁衍子孙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.00,0:17:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有能够留下子孙 机械人才能超越人类
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.89,0:17:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为神
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.61,0:17:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事情怎么可能...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.16,0:17:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理论上是可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.53,0:17:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体组织上与以往的机械人不同
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.45,0:17:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,体内细胞自动增殖的男性机械人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.29,0:17:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将此接纳到自己的身体内 制造出生命体的女性机械人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.33,0:17:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是卡辛、迪奥和莱妲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.66,0:17:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以卡辛是不死之身？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.85,0:17:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这不是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.10,0:17:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这3个机械人都是失败之作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.12,0:17:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能作为拥有强韧身躯的杀戮兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.80,0:18:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀戮...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.96,0:18:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只不过是杀戮兵器吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.39,0:18:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为不死之身的原因不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.74,0:18:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是杀死露娜之后发生的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.64,0:18:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 露娜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.84,0:18:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许一切都是自从那个女人出现开始的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.33,0:18:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露娜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.51,0:18:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被称为 名为月的太阳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.50,0:18:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有永恒的生命 被所有人所爱戴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.03,0:18:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治愈、分出生命给大家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.02,0:18:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是露娜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.22,0:18:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是君临世界的人只能有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.22,0:18:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天无二日
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.02,0:18:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我下命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.79,0:19:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀死露娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.32,0:19:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀死... 露娜...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.78,0:19:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡辛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.39,0:19:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把露娜...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.22,0:19:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀死...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.96,0:19:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡辛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.67,0:20:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 卡辛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.67,0:20:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀死... 露娜...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.58,0:20:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是卡辛的错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.06,0:20:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.77,0:20:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.91,0:20:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.77,0:21:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.34,0:21:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡辛！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.94,0:21:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样做的话卡辛会死的！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.85,0:21:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.54,0:21:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！ 不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.49,0:21:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是卡辛的错！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.18,0:21:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是卡辛的错！ 不是卡辛的错！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.73,0:21:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 这样下去真的会死的！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.71,0:21:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 所以 请住手！ 卡辛！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.09,0:21:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不行！ 不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===ED_EP13===
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.36,0:22:12.08,ED_EP13,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}君よ　その幼き笑顔の
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.38,0:22:18.08,ED_EP13,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}汚れ無き瞳（め）に映る自分を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.40,0:22:24.00,ED_EP13,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}迷うことなく　ただ真っすぐに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.37,0:22:30.02,ED_EP13,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}見つめ返すこと　出来るのか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.11,0:22:41.36,ED_EP13,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}巻き戻せない　瞬間の連鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.18,0:22:45.96,ED_EP13,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}ただ、未来へと　延びてゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.19,0:22:51.84,ED_EP13,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}君よ　怒れる風になれ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.21,0:22:57.94,ED_EP13,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}やさしく瞬く星になれ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.22,0:23:03.85,ED_EP13,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}君の内で目覚めた希望（ヒカリ）が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.21,0:23:07.11,ED_EP13,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}映し出すよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.73,0:23:11.41,ED_EP13,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}蒼い影
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===NEXT===
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.21,0:23:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有着无法逃避的往事之人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.74,0:23:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有伴随着真相一起前进
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.71,0:23:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 真相照亮黑暗